### TC09 - empId trong path variable bị trống
PATCH http://localhost:9004/api/v1/installation-forms/assign/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

{
  "formCode": "FORMC-2026-001",
  "formNumber": "FNUM-2026-001"
}

> {%
client.test("Status is 404 (Endpoint not found)", function() {
  client.assert(response.status === 404);
});
%}


### TC10 - formCode chứa ký tự đặc biệt (SQL Injection attempt)
PATCH http://localhost:9004/api/v1/installation-forms/assign/EMP001
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

{
  "formCode": "FORMC' OR 1=1 --",
  "formNumber": "FNUM-2026-001"
}

> {%
client.test("Status is 400 or 404 (Business exception)", function() {
  client.assert(response.status === 400 || response.status === 404);
});
%}


### TC11 - Không có quyền truy cập (Missing Authorization header)
PATCH http://localhost:9004/api/v1/installation-forms/assign/EMP001
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "formCode": "FORMC-2026-001",
  "formNumber": "FNUM-2026-001"
}

> {%
client.test("Status is 401", function() {
  client.assert(response.status === 401);
});
%}


### TC12 - Quyền truy cập không hợp lệ (Role not authorized - e.g. SURVEY_STAFF)
PATCH http://localhost:9004/api/v1/installation-forms/assign/EMP001
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{invalid_role_token}}

{
  "formCode": "FORMC-2026-001",
  "formNumber": "FNUM-2026-001"
}

> {%
client.test("Status is 403", function() {
  client.assert(response.status === 403);
});
%}


